{"tid":1848406,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府唔肯封關，初四後香港將成疫埠，只剩罷工一途可保命。","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:43:45.000Z","uid":59815,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"736c2c681524a037f13b73ae8ae211b1111e1bb9","tid":1848406,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8STyO6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8STyO6v.png&h=e65bcd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>自我隔離 抗疫罷工</strong></span><br />\n政府唔肯封關，初四後香港將成疫埠，只剩罷工一途可保命。一車車高鐵仍然暢通無阻運到西九高鐵站，旅客「健康申報」形同無物！「#社區爆發」只是時間問題！<br />\n<br />\n打工仔女無謂搵命搏，一方面學生休學到2月中，家長本身已需要密切關顧子女健康，無時間返工。另一方面，香港毫無防疫決心，自己都唔知自己係咪帶菌者，返工真係非常不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n既然政府咁鍾意搞「＃健康申報」，我哋一於向僱主作嚴格「＃健康申報表」，向僱主仔細講述過去14日的行蹤，見過咩人，當中有無人發燒、有感染跡象，是否見過曾往返內地的親友，如果有，自己真係唔會知自己係唔係 #隱性病人，咁點返工呢？<br />\n<br />\n全城 #自我隔離，係有效減低傳染風險、抒緩醫護壓力的方法。政府不封關保港，我哋只能團結自救！ #自我隔離， #抗疫罷工！<br />\n<br />\n✉️自願向僱主作「健康申報」及自我隔離通知書範本：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/health_declare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fhealth_declare&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=15c40006\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/health_declare</a><br />\n<br />\n#standwithmedics<br />\n#standwithHAEA<br />\n#封關保港<br />\n#全城抗疫"},{"pid":"fb283a0190f4375b8481c2ccc81a8bd08f74b1b9","tid":1848406,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpTV157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpTV157.png&h=a77d0703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝7:00 黎明行動 準時點人數</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig